{"tid":1213734,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"想講講八仙水上樂園同浸大件事","createTime":"2019-06-13T02:33:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T03:44:52.000Z","uid":259837,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ae088338d6ede198a7c733773a9570d5b93bc641","tid":1213734,"uid":259837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T02:33:15.000Z","msg":"今個月27號就係八仙樂園件事四週年<br />\n好多人都因為該事而受到重傷，即使喺戶外仍然因為空氣有著太多粉塵而造成意外；<br />\n同時亦不由得諗返起浸大宿舍生日派對用麵粉造成的意外，就只係我地身邊嘅麵粉，再加上火光就可以做到咁嚴重嘅後果，連潑水都只會有反效果。<br />\n<br />\n大家如果有多啲化學常識就好啦。唉"},{"pid":"3c11ddf9802a23bfb107b161efb78ced318d5451","tid":1213734,"uid":259837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T02:36:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7d108f3d8d877de030edf59a3eef8544a5b652e","tid":1213734,"uid":259837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T02:37:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b95a6449e69d67d68e84070fdf5b15a59c1dd1ba","tid":1213734,"uid":191926,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T02:37:30.000Z","msg":"係戶外 用途不大<br />\n呢幾日又濕"},{"pid":"669a33d458eea3ee10a0478a6e75218496b3a91f","tid":1213734,"uid":32722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b95a6449e69d67d68e84070fdf5b15a59c1dd1ba","tid":1213734,"uid":191926,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T02:37:30.000Z","msg":"係戶外 用途不大<br />\n呢幾日又濕"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T02:42:15.000Z","msg":"八仙都係戶外？"},{"pid":"596cd8f292d15835381a6171dc39950ab023588c","tid":1213734,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"669a33d458eea3ee10a0478a6e75218496b3a91f","tid":1213734,"uid":32722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b95a6449e69d67d68e84070fdf5b15a59c1dd1ba","tid":1213734,"uid":191926,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T02:37:30.000Z","msg":"係戶外 用途不大<br />\n呢幾日又濕"},"citedBy":1,